org.hibernate.query.spi

Class ResultSetMappingDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.spi.ResultSetMappingDescriptor

  • public class ResultSetMappingDescriptor
extends Object
    Keep a description of the SqlResultSetMapping Note that we do not track joins/fetches here as we do in the manual approach as this feature is defined by JPA and we simply support the JPA feature here. Note also that we track the result builders here (as opposed to the QueryResult) to better fit with NativeQuery which is where this is ultimately used.
